title: Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy 1981 576p AC3 2.0 HEVC
description: All 6 episodes of BBC's Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy encoded in HEVC/x265 at very high quality settings for the best possible experience from the original DVD's Don't Panic all extras from the bonus disk are included. Note the audio is AC3 2.0 but there are two tracks. One is Stereo, the other is Mono (in spite of the fact they are both dual channel). http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0081874/ See you all at Millyways
